@@ -15,14 +15,17 @@ Required properties:
   data randomizer must be supported before an MTD device can be registered.
   Compatibles marked deprecated support only the old bindings described
   at the bottom.
-- reg: NAND flash controller memory area.
+- reg: NAND flash controller memory area. Berlin2CD also requires the pBridge
+  memory area as its second entry.
+- reg-names: required for Berlin2CD and shall contain "nfc" and "pbridge".
 - #address-cells: shall be set to 1. Encode the NAND CS.
 - #size-cells: shall be set to 0.
 - interrupts: shall define the NAND controller interrupt.
-- clocks: shall reference the NAND controller clocks, the second one is
